      hackathon](https://metagame.substack.com/p/fork-the-world-opening-), two MetaFests
      ([1](https://metagame.substack.com/p/metaspecial-metafest-is-alive) &
      [2](https://metagame.substack.com/p/metafest2-is-happening-now)) & countless meetups all in the metaverse, we‚Äôve
      decided to level up & organize IRL!
    </Markdown>

    <Markdown>
      [MetaGame](https://metagame.wtf) is an EVM based coordination game kickstarted by MetaCartel. A decentralized
      factory & a [network of projects](https://metagame.wtf/guilds) currently concerned with onboarding people into the
      DAO space.
    </Markdown>

